<section id="about-me" class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-photo-container">
                <dotlottie-player 
                    src="https://lottie.host/e9bb1186-c7f4-4181-8a73-bdff02f8440c/WCRkGPlthD.lottie" 
                    background="transparent" 
                    speed="1" 
                    loop 
                    autoplay>
                </dotlottie-player>
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dqbxkmkph/image/upload/v1759879976/ANaM_ynwj0v.png" alt="Ana Maria Posada">
            </div>
            <div class="text-left">
                <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Meet Ana Maria</h2>
            <div class="text-left max-w-3xl">

    <p class="text-base md:text-lg md:leading-7 mb-3 font-normal">
        <strong>Ana Maria</strong> is a Colombian <strong>multidisciplinary designer</strong> based in <strong>Vancouver, Canada</strong> with the soul of a musician and the heart of an artist. She blends her background in <strong>Social Communication</strong> and <strong>Digital Design</strong> to transform complex ideas into clear, engaging products. Her path has led her from <strong>independent clients</strong> to creative agencies like <strong>Rethink</strong> and global companies like <strong>IBM</strong> and <strong>Electronic Arts (EA)</strong>, where she served as a <strong>Production Designer</strong> delivering high-quality assets for their digital platforms.
    </p>

    <p class="text-base md:text-lg md:leading-7 mb-3 font-normal">
        Specializing in <strong>UI/UX</strong> and <strong>Web Design</strong>, Ana Maria offers a <strong>total creative package</strong> that includes everything from <strong>brand identity</strong> to <strong>videography</strong> and <strong>motion graphics</strong>. As well as a <strong>music producer and singer-songwriter</strong>, she brings a natural sense of rhythm and flow to her digital work. By combining <strong>AI-powered tools</strong> with her <strong>artistic brain</strong>, she ensures every design is stunning but serves its purpose, focusing on creating accessible <strong>user experiences</strong> that feel engaging and intuitive.
    </p>
</div>
